{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.080", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.720", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.080", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe mir als Sch\u00fcler mit Nachhilfe in Deutsch ein paar Euros dazuverdient. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.840", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass ich das als Abgeordneter einmal in diesem Hohen Hause f\u00fcr eine Fraktion tun w\u00fcrde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.840", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die neu hinzugekommen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.000", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "h\u00e4tte ich mir nicht tr\u00e4umen lassen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.360", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer fremde Sprachen nicht kennt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.840", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wei\u00df nichts von seiner eigenen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.960", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was h\u00e4tte Goethe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.720", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von dem dieser Ausspruch stammt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wohl zu Ihrem Gesetzentwurf gesagt?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.120", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin mir sicher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.000", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er h\u00e4tte sich gesch\u00e4mt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.440", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sprechen von \u201eVerdr\u00e4ngung der deutschen Sprache\u201c und davon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Deutsch das \u201eprim\u00e4re Mittel zur Verst\u00e4ndigung der Deutschen\u201c sei. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.560", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade deshalb sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.760", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wer das Grundgesetz nicht kennt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.280", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verdammt noch mal die Finger davon lassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.960", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daran Ver\u00e4nderungen vornehmen zu wollen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie verkennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.080", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Grundgesetz Grundrechte nicht nur f\u00fcr Deutsche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern f\u00fcr alle Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.760", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in seinem Geltungsbereich leben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.840", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "festschreibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.160", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch verkennen Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Deutsch im In- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Ausland gesprochen wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht umsonst ist das Goethe-Institut mit 159\u00a0Einrichtungen in 98\u00a0L\u00e4ndern gegenw\u00e4rtig und vermittelt die deutsche Sprache und die deutsche Kultur."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber welches Deutsch eigentlich? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.200", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Deutsch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.160", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wir heute sprechen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.960", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist nicht einmal mehr das Deutsch von vor 20\u00a0Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von den \u00fcber 50\u00a0Mundarten mal ganz zu schweigen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.040", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Sprache ist eine Summe aus den grundrechtlich zugestandenen Freiheiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.240", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eigene Pers\u00f6nlichkeit frei zu entfalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.880", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unsere Verfassung ist dem gesellschaftlichen Wandel gegen\u00fcber aufgeschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.560", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genauso ist es mit der deutschen Sprache. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.560", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese in einen idealen Zustand pressen und bewahren zu wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.760", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00e4me der ungerechtfertigten Einschr\u00e4nkung von Grundrechten gleich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Anliegen der AfD-Fraktion ist daher viel weniger redlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als uns der Gesetzentwurf glauben zu machen versucht; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.480", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn er sch\u00fcrt \u00c4ngste,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.520", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00c4ngste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.000", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die jeder Grundlage entbehren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.080", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00c4ngste, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.920", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne die eine AfD in Deutschland ihre Anh\u00e4ngerschaft verl\u00f6re."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Gesetzentwurf zeichnet dar\u00fcber hinaus ein unwahres, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.000", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein d\u00fcsteres Bild. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.560", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es klingt beinahe nach dem Eintritt des Verteidigungsfalles, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.640", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man Ihrer Sachverhaltsdarstellung folgt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.640", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass demn\u00e4chst Anglizismen unsere deutsche Sprache \u00fcbernehmen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielmehr l\u00f6sen Sie durch diese b\u00f6sartigen Unterstellungen den demokratischen Verteidigungsfall aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit der Mehrheit dieses Hohen Hauses verteidigen wir die Menschen vor Ihnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.480", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die mit ihrer eigenen deutschen Sprache die kulturelle Vielfalt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.040", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Wissenschaft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.520", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Miteinander in diesem Land f\u00f6rdern als Ausfluss ihres allgemeinen Pers\u00f6nlichkeitsrechtes."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Keiner der Anwesenden wird ernsthaft bestreiten k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.440", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die deutsche Sprache schon jetzt verfassungsrechtliche Bedeutung hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.880", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Grundgesetz der Bundesrepublik Deutschland ist schlie\u00dflich auf Deutsch verfasst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch da kann ich Ihnen gerne Nachhilfe geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.840", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn Sie diese ben\u00f6tigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Geltung des deutschen Grundgesetzes bedeutet zugleich die Geltung der deutschen Sprache. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.400", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie genie\u00dft somit Verfassungsrang. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.600", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lesen bildet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.601", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.601", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.440", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Geltungsbereich unseres Grundgesetzes leben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.640", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen sich daher die deutsche Sprache aneignen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.480", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ohne die deutsche Sprache sind sie vor Beh\u00f6rden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vor Gericht und in der demokratischen Auseinandersetzung unterlegen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.640", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur wer die Sprache der Verfassung des Landes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.520", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dem er lebt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.040", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beherrscht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.800", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "findet Schutz und eine Heimat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.960", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oder mit Goethe:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.480", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Deutsche soll alle Sprachen lernen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.640", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit ihm zu Hause kein Fremder unbequem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.680", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er aber in der Fremde \u00fcberall zu Hause sei."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.120", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kurzum: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.040", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Grundgesetz in deutscher Sprache braucht einen solchen Zusatz nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.120", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am Niederrhein h\u00e4tte man Ihnen wahrscheinlich nur gesagt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.480", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da ham\u2019 die Schwadron\u00f6res ma\u2019 wieder Stuss zusammengefrickelt!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.200", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt erteile ich dem Kollegen Stephan Thomae, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.880", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "FDP-Fraktion, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.960", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}